<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4323308391322690693">Samantha Bruce-Benjamin is the author of <i>The Art of Devotion</i>, an <i>Examiner</i> and <i>Bookreporter</i> Best Book of 2010. Born and raised in Edinburgh, Scotland, she holds a Master of Arts with Honors in English Literature from The University of Edinburgh. A former Random House and BBC literary editor, she divides her time between New York and Edinburgh, where she is currently reading for a PhD in Creative Wr</span>
  <span id="freeText4323308391322690693" style="display:none">Samantha Bruce-Benjamin is the author of <i>The Art of Devotion</i>, an <i>Examiner</i> and <i>Bookreporter</i> Best Book of 2010. Born and raised in Edinburgh, Scotland, she holds a Master of Arts with Honors in English Literature from The University of Edinburgh. A former Random House and BBC literary editor, she divides her time between New York and Edinburgh, where she is currently reading for a PhD in Creative Writing at The University of Edinburgh.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4323308391322690693" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
